OL,6,FA , commissioned by the supermarket,
OL,7,Fand written by Professor of
OL,8,FCriminology at City, University of
OL,9,FLondon, Emmeline Taylor, found that
OL,10,Fstaff are facing an "alarming"
OL,11,Fincrease in crime, violence,
OL,12,Fintimidation and abuse.
OL,14,FThere were more than 300,000 incidents
OL,15,Fof shoplifting, abuse, violence and
OL,16,Fanti-social behaviour in Co-op stores
OL,17,Flast year, the report found.
OL,19,FThe number of assaults increased by a
OL,20,Fthird to more than 1,300.
