OL,6,FMatt Hood, managing director of Co-op
OL,7,FFood, said: "We are seeing far too
OL,8,Fmany prolific offenders persistently
OL,9,Fsteal large volumes of products, in
OL,10,Four shops every day, and, if they are
OL,11,Fstealing to fund addictions, the
OL,12,Fsituation often becomes volatile and
OL,13,Fdangerous.
OL,15,FMr Hood urged the government to not
OL,16,F"turn their backs" on staff, who are
OL,17,Foften faced with "volatile" and
OL,18,F"dangerous" situations.
