OL,6,FThe amendment to the Criminal Justice
OL,7,FBill is soon to be debated in
OL,8,FParliament. The offence would carry a
OL,9,Fsentence of 12 months behind bars or a
OL,10,Ffine of up to #10,000.
OL,12,FIn an interview with ITV News, the
OL,13,Fauthor of the report, Ms Taylor,
OL,14,Foutlined a 10-point plan of
OL,15,Frecommendations to help curb the abuse
OL,16,Fand violence.
OL,18,F"One of those recommendations is to
OL,19,Ftarget the stolen goods market," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
